<ext_description linkend="Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network_arm.Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network">
A <b>Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network</b> is a mean to provide information about the <b>implementation</b> of a connectivity requirement to a network.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network_arm.Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network.connectivity_requirement">
specifies the <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping:arm:Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping_arm.Aggregate_connectivity_requirement"/> for the 
<b>Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network_arm.Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network.implementation">
specifies the <express_ref linkend="Layered_interconnect_module_design:arm:Layered_interconnect_module_design_arm.Generic_physical_network"/> for the <b>Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network_arm.Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network.ur:UR1">
The <b>implementation</b> shall be unique within a population of <b>Connectivity_allocation_to_physical_network</b>.
</ext_description>
